text: Darlinghurst is an inner-city (central point of the city) and suburb of Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. Darlinghurst is east of the Sydney central business district (CBD) and Hyde Park, within the local government area of the City of Sydney.Gregory's Sydney Street Directory, Gregory's Publishing Company, 2007 It is often by the nickname "Darlo". ==References== Category:Suburbs of Sydney
title: Darlinghurst, New South Wales
